<tr ><td colspan="3" align="left" valign="top" style="padding-left:35px; padding-right:35px; padding-bottom:25px; " ><div class="mktEditable" id="text2" ><h2>MCS-3000/6000 Upgrade to MCS-4000/7000 Promotional Pricing and Trade-In</h2>
<h2><span style="color: #191a00; font-size: 12px; line-height: 14.3999996185303px;">Below you will find the link for Honeywell's Sales Bulletin 2015-18 Rev A:</span></h2>
<p><a href="https://pages3.honeywell.com/rs/honeywell3/images/2015-18 Rev A_MCS-3000_6000 Upgrade Promotion.pdf">2015-18 Rev A_MCS-3000_6000 Upgrade Promotion.pdf</a></p>
<p>The purpose of this bulletin is to provide discounted pricing for upgrading an MCS-3000/6000 Satcom to an MCS-4000/7000.</p>
<p><strong>Rev A Notes:&nbsp;</strong>Updated Table 1-1 and incorporated Table 1-2 in Sec 4.0. Removed MCS 4200 information.</p>
<p><span style="line-height: 14.3999996185303px;">This bulletin will be sent via e-mail to Honeywell Dealers on Thursday, May 21st, 2015.</span></p>
<p>Sales Bulletins are also available in the <a href="http://teamsites.honeywell.com/sites/BGAsales/Pages/2015SalesBulletins.aspx">BGA toolkit </a>(Internal Only)</p>
<p>Dealers can find 2015 sales bulletins in the new Honeywell Aerospace Website&nbsp;or in <a href="https://commerce.honeywell.com/webapp/wcs/stores/servlet/HonSalesBulletinView?storeId=10651" target="_blank">MyAerospace</a> under sales bulletins.</p></div>
